{"tid":737864,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"臥底揭插贓拉人交差 五警涉妨礙司法公正被捕","createTime":"2018-07-11T06:18:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-11T06:28:52.000Z","uid":148652,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c58b6a40943b2a4aeeb36d3d5a690afd44fa5c26","tid":737864,"uid":148652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T06:18:43.000Z","msg":"警方有組織罪案及三合會調查科拘捕五名警務人員及兩名男子，懷疑他們串謀妨礙司法公正。O記兩年前派臥底滲入荃灣和勝和，揭發該黑幫設控制中心「收Call派毒」及實時遙控販毒，O記早前「收網」拘捕六十三人。<span style=\"color: red;\">不過，案件續有下文，該名臥底探員在滲入黑幫期間，有反黑警員招攬他作為線人，該臥底其後踼爆反黑警員涉嫌在查案期間插贓設局，務求拉人交差。</span>O記昨晨拘捕一名警長、四名警員及兩名男子，據悉，五人隸屬荃灣警區反三合會行動組，已被停職。<br />\n<br />\nLaughed,古惑仔拉唔到，就拉返自己人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96e0947e1bf086f145ab081b1b22ba6d6310f293","tid":737864,"uid":132587,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T06:19:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://i.imgur.com/DH7f8RX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FDH7f8RX.jpg&h=c0325716&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e074f711bb8ea9757c49a2178a02b638e8b660f7","tid":737864,"uid":55924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T06:26:16.000Z","msg":"拉自己卧底都算係拉左人 closed file"},{"pid":"2d1bdc564138006345100ef2f866cac78fdff62f","tid":737864,"uid":45185,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-11T06:28:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/11/142841_091c8ef9e0b7b611d377da62dbbd22ea.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F11%2F142841_091c8ef9e0b7b611d377da62dbbd22ea.png&h=54f239b1&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}